reviewText: Great comedian but should never put a DVD together on his own. Didn't even keep the DVD. Waste of money

This is a pretty OK DVD. Its not the highest quality in editing or A/V but it is still entertaining at the least.  I did not expect much from it being it was made a while ago, but it was good for a few laughs.

Perhaps I'm getting a bit jaded.
Some of these comedians don't move me at all
Tried watching this and it couldn't keep my interest
